  <!-- DESCRIPTION MAKER with VANILLA FALLBACKS -->
  <RulePackDef>
    <defName>BNF_MusicDescription</defName>
    <label>BNF music description (expanded)</label>
    <rulePack>
      <rulesStrings>
        <!-- Root (always 5 sentences: genre -> art1 -> art2 -> art3 -> quality) -->
        <li>r_art_description->[bnf_desc5]</li>
        <li>bnf_desc5->[bnf_genre_intro] [bnf_art1] [bnf_art2] [bnf_art3] [bnf_quality_line]</li>

        <!-- 1) Genre intro -->
        <li>bnf_genre_intro->This is a [bnf_genre] recording captured on magnetic microtape.</li>
        <li>bnf_genre_intro->A [bnf_genre] session preserved on a worn cartridge.</li>
        <li>bnf_genre_intro->An archive of [bnf_genre] committed to microtape storage.</li>
        <li>bnf_genre_intro->Recovered [bnf_genre] material pressed into a fragile cartridge.</li>

        <!-- Genres (base pool + Cowboy Bebop reference) -->
        <li>bnf_genre->rock|jazz|classical|folk|rap|lo-fi|electronic|ambient|blues|country|metal|punk|soul|funk|industrial|post-rock|drone|experimental|western bebop</li>

        <!-- 2–4) Art-style lines -->
        <li>bnf_art1->Motifs [bnf_motion] while [bnf_subject] [bnf_action] [bnf_space].</li>
        <li>bnf_art1->It sketches [bnf_poetic_image], and [bnf_subject] keeps time with [bnf_space].</li>
        <li>bnf_art1->Fragments overlap like [bnf_poetic_image], then settle into a slow pattern.</li>
        <li>bnf_art1->Themes rise, [bnf_motion_verb] against [bnf_space] until they dissolve.</li>

        <li>bnf_art2->A figure returns again and again, [bnf_motion_verb] at the edge of silence.</li>
        <li>bnf_art2->Between takes, you can almost hear [bnf_scene_detail].</li>
        <li>bnf_art2->Lines blur; themes [bnf_motion_verb] and reform.</li>
        <li>bnf_art2->It paints [bnf_poetic_image], only to have it vanish into static.</li>

        <li>bnf_art3->The performance feels [bnf_mood], as if recorded [bnf_place].</li>
        <li>bnf_art3->Despite the roughness, a [bnf_color] thread holds it together.</li>
        <li>bnf_art3->It sways between [bnf_mood_a] and [bnf_mood_b].</li>
        <li>bnf_art3->The arrangement seems [bnf_mood], echoing across [bnf_space].</li>

        <!-- Expanded art pools -->
        <li>bnf_subject->the melody|the rhythm|the harmony|the voice|the ensemble|the arrangement|the guitar|the synths|the percussion|the bassline|the brass|the strings</li>
        <li>bnf_action->threads through|cuts across|rises over|flickers between|presses against|falls back into|loops around|circles|collides with|hums beneath|resonates with|erupts against</li>
        <li>bnf_space->a low hum of machinery|the thrum of colony life|radio noise|quiet corridors|the open sky|the hull’s metal echo|a slow room reverb|stone walls|a generator drone|the night wind|steel scaffolds|cargo crates stacked high|dusty caverns|dormitory bunks</li>

        <li>bnf_poetic_image->radio static over empty plains|dust drifting in projector light|wind across broken antennae|glowtubes humming at shift change|river water in moonlight|machinery echoing down long halls|a storm creeping over steel roofs|a lullaby half-remembered|the shimmer of heat above rock|a lantern guttering in the dark|cracked speakers buzzing|shadows cast by neon signs</li>

        <li>bnf_motion->drift toward memory|spill into corners|circle the room|bloom and fade|stumble then steady|scatter like leaves|linger at the edges|pulse unevenly</li>
        <li>bnf_motion_verb->drift|bloom|shiver|converge|unravel|fracture|dissolve|spiral</li>

        <li>bnf_scene_detail->chairs being moved|someone counting off|a cough near the mic|footsteps in the hall|faint wind at the door|gear warming up|an engineer adjusting dials|a match being struck|murmurs before silence</li>

        <li>bnf_mood->restless|unhurried|tense|intimate|searching|hypnotic|somber|bright|jubilant|melancholy|agitated|ethereal|grounded|chaotic</li>
        <li>bnf_place->in a cargo bay|under the dome|in a basement room|beside the river|in an empty barracks|inside a maintenance tunnel|at a forgotten outpost|within a mining shaft|beneath flickering lights</li>
        <li>bnf_color->silver|copper|amber|indigo|crimson|emerald|violet|golden|ashen</li>
        <li>bnf_mood_a->calm|melancholy|resolve|unease|joy|chaos|clarity|suspense</li>
        <li>bnf_mood_b->noise|anticipation|regret|heat|clarity|stillness|despair|warmth</li>

        <!-- 5) Audio quality (expanded) -->
        <li>bnf_quality_line->The fidelity is [bnf_texture], with moments of [bnf_texture_detail] peeking through.</li>
        <li>bnf_quality_line->Overall it sounds [bnf_texture]; at times the transfer reveals [bnf_texture_detail].</li>
        <li>bnf_quality_line->Expect a [bnf_texture] character; occasional passages bloom with [bnf_texture_detail].</li>
        <li>bnf_quality_line->It carries a [bnf_texture] edge, softened only by flashes of [bnf_texture_detail].</li>

        <li>bnf_texture->thin|muddy|harsh|warbly|fluttering|uneven|compressed|airy|clear|balanced|saturated|narrow|wide|tinny|grainy|crisp|distorted|warm|cold|fragile</li>
        <li>bnf_texture_detail->tape warmth|unexpected clarity|soft hiss|room bloom|metallic shimmer|low-end smear|tight focus|gentle print-through|sharp transients|deep resonance|residual hum</li>
      </rulesStrings>
    </rulePack>
  </RulePackDef>

</Defs>
